---
import Layout from "@/components/Layout.astro"
import Globe from "@/components/Globe.astro"
import Photostrip from "@/components/Photostrip.astro"
import { response } from "@/src/pages/projects.astro"
import type { Project } from "@/src/pages/projects.astro"
import Card from "@/components/Card.astro"
import Polaroid from "@/components/Polaroid.astro"

const firstPlace = response.filter((project: Project) => project.fields.project_name == "Catatime: Fill Your Coding Cup")[0]
const secondPlace = response.filter((project: Project) => project.fields.project_name == "Synthena")[0]
const thirdPlace = response.filter((project: Project) => project.fields.project_name == "rate my rizz")[0]

const photos = [{
	"url": "photostrip-1.JPG",
	"description": "Attendees on the MTA (New York's subway)"
},
{
	"url": "photostrip-2.png",
	"description": "test"
}]

const photos_2 = [{
	"url": "photostrip-3.jpg",
	"description": "Two attendees showing off their code."
},
{
	"url": "photostrip-4.jpeg",
	"description": "test"
}]

const polaroids = [
	{"url": "https://hc-cdn.hel1.your-objectstorage.com/s/v3/1d4744e76819a2e040cf6b3e9b3026d740218677_image.png", "description": "don't mind the celsius?!", "className": "rotate-12"},
	{"url": "https://hc-cdn.hel1.your-objectstorage.com/s/v3/c0962c010ed0cc123e0e6adab551fd0b15666469_image.png", "description": "locked in", "className": "-rotate-12"},
	{"url": "https://hc-cdn.hel1.your-objectstorage.com/s/v3/1b98c074f2431bb2bd9d28f969536ca1e7d1555f_image.png", "description": "out and about in new york city", "className": "-rotate-[8deg]"},
	{"url": "https://hc-cdn.hel1.your-objectstorage.com/s/v3/ef872169d20d5bd8fd37eaa526bff98c7012685e_image.png", "description": "ðŸ“¸", "className": "rotate-[20deg]"},
	{"url": "https://hc-cdn.hel1.your-objectstorage.com/s/v3/d134154c13511e14554c1074194f8b29ca88d566_image.png", "description": "demo time!", "className": "rotate-0"},
]

---
<Layout>
	<a href="https://hackclub.com/"><img class = "absolute top-5 left-0 w-48 md:w-64 z-30" src="https://assets.hackclub.com/banners/2025.svg" alt="Hack Club"/></a>
	<div class = "relative h-screen top-0 flex flex-col justify-center w-full">
		<div class = "inset-0 absolute bg-center bg-cover" style = "background-image: url('/background.jpg')"></div>
		<div class = "absolute bg-cover inset-0 bg-linear-to-b via-70% via-theme-green-darker/85 from-theme-green-darker/80 to-black/70 z-20"></div>
	<img src = "left-paper-corner.png" class = "absolute top-0 md:h-8/12"/>
	<img src = "right-paper-corner.png" class = "absolute md:h-8/12 bottom-0 right-0"/>
	<section class = "z-30 w-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-2">
		<p class = "text-outline">3-day hackathon in New York City</p>
		<div class = "bg-[url('s-vine.png')] drop-shadow-[0_0_48px_rgba(219,196,145,0.8)] bg-center bg-no-repeat bg-cover w-6/7 md:w-4/7">
			<img class = "mx-auto w-full md:w-11/12" src = "logo.png"/>
		</div>
		<p class = "text-outline">November 14th-16th 2025</p>
	</section>
	</div>

	<div class = "h-full relative">
		<div class="min-h-screen absolute inset-0 opacity-40" style = "background-image: url(background.svg)"></div>
		<section class = "bg-linear-to-b from-black via-25% to-theme-green-darker flex flex-row">
			<img src="column.png" class="absolute rotate-90 z-20 w-screen scale-[calc(16%*-1)_calc(15%*-1)] -translate-y-6/12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"/>  
			<img src="small-vine-1.png" class="basis-3/12 w-4/12 h-6/12"/>
			<div class = "w-11/12 pt-20">
				<div class = "flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-20 not-first:hidden">
					<div>
						<h1 class = "text-center">For three days in mid-November...</h1>
						<p class = "text-center text-2xl">126 teen programmers from 15 different countries gathered at Duolingo HQ, then at Civic Hall in <span class = "text-highlight">Manhattan, NYC.</span></p>
					</div>
					<div class = "hidden lg:inline">
						<Globe/>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<img src = "small-vine-2.png" class = "basis-3/12 w-4/12 h-7/12"/>
		</section>

		<section class = "bg-theme-green-darker h-[145vh] sm:h-[130vh] md:max-lg:h-[140vh] lg:h-[80vh]">
			<div class = "flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-center">
				<div class = "w-full overflow-hidden">
					<Photostrip photos = {photos} className = "-rotate-12 translate-x-8 sm:max-lg:translate-x-32 md:max-lg:translate-x-64 translate-y-12 lg:translate-x-16 z-0"/>
					<Photostrip photos = {photos_2} className = "rotate-12 translate-x-64 sm:max-lg:translate-x-64 md:max-lg:translate-x-110 lg:translate-x-50 -translate-y-64 lg:-translate-y-48 z-20"/>
				</div>
				<div class = "w-8/12 -translate-y-48 lg:-translate-y-32 lg:basis-2/3 text-center mx-16 md:max-lg:mr-20 lg:mr-40">
					<img src = "gold-vine.png" class = "w-1/2 mx-auto"/>
					<h1>40 hours of hacking</h1>
					<p>From Friday night to Sunday morning, attendees spent hours hacking away at their Parthenon projects. Teens built everything from <a target = "_blank" href = "/projects#Date_The_Duo">multiplayer dating sim games</a> to <a target = "_blank" href = "/projects#arDJuino">Arduino-controlled DJ sets</span>.</p>
					<a class = "my-4 bg-theme-cream border p-4 block w-full md:w-1/2 mx-auto text-theme-green-darker text-center text-3xl" href = "/projects">
						view all projects
					</a>
					<img src = "gold-vine.png" class = "w-1/2 mx-auto rotate-180"/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class = "h-[280vh] md:h-[240vh] lg:h-[120vh] bg-linear-to-t from-black via-25% to-theme-green-darker flex flex-col p-10 md:p-20 text-center">
				<h1>54 projects (and countless memories) made.</h1>
				<p>At 8am on Sunday, attendees rushed to make sure their projects were shipped and working in time for the project showcase, which was attended by engineers at companies such as GitHub, Notion, Slack and Cloudflare.</p>
				<p>The top three projects were determined through peer voting.</p>
				<div class = "grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 items-center justify-center h-full">
					{[firstPlace, secondPlace, thirdPlace].map((project: Project, index: number) => 
					<div class = "flex flex-col gap-4 items-center justify-center h-full">
						<h2>{index + 1}.</h2>
						<Card project = {project} className = "w-full z-40" descriptionCap={90}/>
					</div>
					)}
				</div>
		</section>

		<section class = "bg-linear-to-b from-black via-25% to-theme-green-darker h-max z-30 pt-10 pb-20">
			<div class = "max-xs:pt-32 py-10 flex justify-around flex-row flex-wrap overflow-hidden">
				{polaroids.map((polaroid: any) => (
					<Polaroid url = {polaroid.url} description = {polaroid.description} className={polaroid.className}/>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>

	</div>

	<div class = "relative h-9/12 top-0 flex flex-col w-full">
		<div class = "inset-0 absolute bg-center bg-cover" style = "background-image: url('/crowd.JPG')"></div>
		<div class = "absolute bg-cover inset-0 bg-linear-to-b via-70% via-theme-green-darker/85 from-theme-green-darker/80 to-black/70 z-20"></div>
		<section class = "h-9/12 flex flex-col top-0 left-0 md:flex-row gap-4 z-30">
		<div class = "bg-theme-cream/80 basis-1/2 p-6 md:p-10 *:text-theme-green-darker">
			<div class = "border-2 border-theme-green-darker p-6 w-full h-full [&>span]:text-lg [&>span]:md:text-2xl [&>span]:block text-center">
				<h1 class = "text-2xl md:text-4xl break-all">Parthenon</h1>
				<span>Parthenon was hosted by Hack Club as part of the <a target = "_blank" href = "https://athena.hackclub.com">Athena Initiative</a> for girls and nonbinary students worldwide. Food and accommodation were provided, with over 20k USD of travel grants being distributed to attendees.</span>
				<br/>
				<br/>
				<span>Prior to coming to Parthenon, attendees spent 30 hours coding and built 3 technical projects as part of the <a target = "_blank" href = "https://award.athena.hackclub.com">Athena Award</a>, a program ran in collaboration with GirlsWhoCode, MIT Beaverworks, and many more.</span>
			</div>
		</div>
		<img class = "hidden absolute md:inline bottom-0 right-10 h-48" src = "yessa_sign_transparent.png"/>
	</section>
	</div>
</Layout>
